summary: In the NHL, history was made as Nordh became the first player to sign with the Utah Hockey Club. In the thrilling Stanley Cup Final, the Edmonton Oilers forced a historic Game 7 after a comeback win in Game 6. Comedian and impressionist Mark Friend was announced as the host for the 2024 NHL Awards. The Oilers made NHL history by scoring eight goals in Game 5 to avoid elimination. In the mock 2024 NHL Draft, experts debated the top prospects after Celebrini and Levshunov were selected with the first two picks. The New York Rangers waived forward Barclay Goodrow. Oilers captain Connor McDavid set a playoff assists record in Game 4 of the Cup Final, leading his team to a victory. After their dominant performance in Game 5, the Oilers shifted their focus to Game 6, while the Florida Panthers aimed to secure their first championship and the Oilers sought to complete a historic comeback in the series finale on Monday.

name: Taylor Wily
summary: Taylor Wily, an actor known for his roles in the popular television series "Hawaii Five-0" and the comedy film "Forgetting Sarah Marshall," has passed away at the age of 56.
